  "title": "Finance Assistant",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Finance Assistant</strong></u></p><p>🚗 Industry: Financial Services</p><p>📍 Location: Newton</p><p>💰 Salary: $2000 - $2800 + VB + Flexi $800 per year</p><p>⏰ Working Hours: Mon to Fri, 8.30am - 5.30pm</p><p><br /></p><p><u><strong>Job Scope:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Support Credit team in basic audit and credit functions such as client monitoring, reviews and follow up.</li><li>Review clients’ accounts receivable, invoices, and financial records to verify authenticity and accuracy.</li><li>Assess clients’ financial position and internal controls to identify irregularities or early warning signals.</li><li>Prepare clear and concise audit reports highlighting findings, risks, and recommendations.</li><li>Ensure adherence to internal audit standards and contribute to continuous process improvement</li><li>10% travel to client sites to conduct audit / credit reviews.</li><li>Any other additional duties as assigned by management.</li></ul><p><u><strong>Requirements:</strong></u></p><ul><li>No experience required, Training will be provided</li><li>Good career prospects and career path</li><li>Minimum any certificate in accounting or business administration, or related field</li><li>Strong analytical and numerical skills</li><li>Attention to detail and accuracy</li><li>Good communication and report writing skills</li><li>Proficiency in MS Excel and Words</li><li>Good working attitude, ability to work with people and willingness to learn.</li><li>Independent, meticulous, reliable, and able to manage tight deadlines or multiple audits concurrently</li></ul><p><br />To apply, please send a copy of your resume to <a href=\"mailto:belindayangsh@antares.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">belindayangsh@antares.com.sg</a></p><p><br /></p><p>By submitting any application or résumé to us, you will be deemed to have agreed and consented to us disclosing your personal information to prospective employers for their consideration.</p><p><br /></p><p>We regret only short-listed candidates will be notified.</p><p><br /></p><p>Belinda Yang Shun Hua</p><p>+65 93476558 | <u>belindayangsh@antares.com.sg</u></p><p>[Antares Management Services Pte Ltd]</p><p>EA: 25C3031 | Reg No. R1110895</p>",
